::KitKat::

She moved out to get a better shot, when the missle came in close.  
She jumped to dodge, but it hit within a few feet of her and  
flattened her to the ground.  She took a few moments, just laying 
there, catching her breath.  She rose to her knees and then got up.  
She found her rifle and limpoed over to Terrorsaur, "They running 
again?"
